CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Rezolute Inc is a biopharmaceutical company. The company develops novel, sustained-release injectable therapies. It applies proprietary formulation and manufacturing capabilities to known, well-characterized molecules to create differentiated, patent-protected therapies that have the potential to significantly improve existing standards of care. Its pipeline products include RZ358 and RZ402.
